c: 4
v: 131
t: "Kananjalo zonke izinto ezisemazulwini nasemhlabeni zezika- Allâh.Yaye Sacebisa aBantu beNcwadi ngaphambili kunani, nakuni maMuslim (Sithi): yoyikani uAllâh nigcine uxanduva lwenu kuYe, kodwa ukuba anikholwa, (yazini okokuba) zonke izinto ezisemazulwini nasemhlabeni zezika-Allâh, kwaye uAllâh Wahlala esisiTyebi, Ufanelwe ziindumiso zonke"